x,y,z\in R
x^2+xy+y^2=1
y^2+yz+z^2=16
xy+yz+zx\leq \frac{16}{3}
16=[(\frac x2+y)^2+\frac 34x^2][(\frac z2+y)^2+\frac 34z^2]
16\ge \frac 34[(\frac x2+y)z+x(y+\frac z2)]^2
\Rightarrow xy+yz+zx\le \frac 8{\sqrt 3}<\frac {16}3
